warp解锁chatGPT和netflix

  • perom
  • 2023年5月7日
  • 未分类

现在比较稳的翻墙工具是naiveproxy, 操作起来也比较简单, 因此选用naiveproxy作为过墙梯子. 这里提一句, naiveproxy实际上是caddy上的一个插件, 因此, 安装naiveproxy时实际上安装的是带naiveproxy插件的caddy. 官方caddy不带naiveproxy插件, 因此需要自己编译带naiveproxy的caddy. 利用naiveproxy过墙后就可以访问大部分的服务了, 但是, 有的服务器IP并不能观看netflix, 或者不能访问chatGPT, 因为观看netflix需要原生IP, 而chatGPT把大部分的主流vps服务商的IP都ban了. 还好cloudflare提供了warp服务, 让流量经过cloudflare, 再访问netflix和chatGPT就可以了. 但是我并不希望naiveproxy的流量都经过warp, 所以我选用v2ray来帮助我分流. 因此, 设计整体的网络拓扑如下:

接下来是安装过程.

安装基本的工具

apt install -y git golang vim

caddy安装

编译带naiveproxy的caddy

naiveproxy的服务器使用caddy作为流量转发 , caddy需要添加插件用于识别naiveproxy流量, 使用如下方法编译带forwardproxy插件的caddy, 其他插件可以参考xcaddy. 编译完后, 在当前目录会生成一个caddy可执行文件.

go install github.com/caddyserver/xcaddy/cmd/xcaddy@latest

~/go/bin/xcaddy build --with github.com/caddyserver/forwardproxy@caddy2=github.com/klzgrad/forwardproxy@naive

配置Caddyfile

新建Caddyfile文件, 并配置转发naiveproxy的流量: 

{
  order forward_proxy before file_server
}
:443, example.com {
  tls me@example.com
  forward_proxy {
    basic_auth user pass
    hide_ip
    hide_via
    probe_resistance
    upstream socks5://127.0.0.1:1080
  }
  file_server {
    root /var/www/html
  }
}

这表示访问example.com的https流量先通过forward_proxy的识别, 如果失败了, 则转到file_server. 可以在/var/www/html部署网站.

  • example.com: 域名
  • user: 鉴权用户名
  • pass: 鉴权密码
    upstream socks5://127.0.0.1:40000 表示将流量输出到socks的1080端口. 目的是将流量重定向到v2ray中, 借助v2ray进行路由.

caddy的systemd服务配置

首先将caddy及配置文件放入合适位置

chmod +x caddy
mv caddy /usr/bin/

mkdir /etc/caddy
mv Caddyfile /etc/caddy/

为caddy单独创建用户和组

groupadd --system caddy

useradd --system \
    --gid caddy \
    --create-home \
    --home-dir /var/lib/caddy \
    --shell /usr/sbin/nologin \
    --comment "Caddy web server" \
    caddy

systemd配置

# file /etc/systemd/system/caddy.service

[Unit]
Description=Caddy
Documentation=https://caddyserver.com/docs/
After=network.target network-online.target
Requires=network-online.target

[Service]
User=caddy
Group=caddy
ExecStart=/usr/bin/caddy run --environ --config /etc/caddy/Caddyfile
ExecReload=/usr/bin/caddy reload --config /etc/caddy/Caddyfile
TimeoutStopSec=5s
LimitNOFILE=1048576
LimitNPROC=512
PrivateTmp=true
ProtectSystem=full
AmbientCapabilities=CAP_NET_BIND_SERVICE

[Install]
WantedBy=multi-user.target

最后启动caddy

systemctl enable --now caddy

安装 v2ray

使用官方推荐脚本安装v2ray

bash <(curl -L https://raw.githubusercontent.com/v2fly/fhs-install-v2ray/master/install-release.sh)

配置 /usr/local/etc/v2ray/config.json

{
  "log": {
    "access": "/var/log/v2ray/access.log",
    "error": "/var/log/v2ray/error.log",
    "loglevel": "warning"
  },
  "inbounds": [{
    "port": 1080,
    "listen": "127.0.0.1",
    "tag": "socks-inbound",
    "protocol": "socks",
    "settings": {
      "auth": "noauth",
      "udp": false
    },

    "sniffing": {
      "enabled": true,
      "destOverride": ["http", "tls"]
    }
  }],
  "outbounds": [{
    "protocol": "freedom",
    "settings": {},
    "tag": "direct"
  },
  {
    "protocol": "socks",
    "settings": {
      "server": [
        {
          "address": "127.0.0.1",
          "port": 40000
        }
      ]
   },
    "tag": "socks5-warp"
  },
  {
    "protocol": "blackhole",
    "settings": {},
    "tag": "blocked"
  }],

  "routing": {
    "domainStrategy": "IPOnDemand",
    "rules":[
      {
        "type": "field",
        "ip": ["geoip:private"],
        "outboundTag": "blocked"
      },
      {
        "type": "field",
        "domain": ["geosite:category-ads"],
        "outboundTag": "blocked"
      },
      {
        "type": "field",
        "domain": [
          "ai.com",
          "chat.openai.com",
          "openai.com",
          "api.openai.com",
          "geosite:netflix"
        ],
        "outboundTag": "socks5-warp"
      },
      {
        "type": "field",
        "ip": [
          "geoip:cn"
        ],
        "outboundTag": "socks5-warp"
      }
    ]
  },

  "dns": {
    "hosts": {
      "domain:v2fly.org": "www.vicemc.net",
      "domain:github.io": "pages.github.com",
      "domain:wikipedia.org": "www.wikimedia.org",
      "domain:shadowsocks.org": "electronicsrealm.com"
    },
    "servers": [
      "1.1.1.1",
      {
        "address": "114.114.114.114",
        "port": 53,
        "domains": [
          "geosite:cn"
        ]
      },
      "8.8.8.8",
      "localhost"
    ]
  },

  "policy": {
    "levels": {
      "0": {
        "uplinkOnly": 0,
        "downlinkOnly": 0
      }
    },
    "system": {
      "statsInboundUplink": false,
      "statsInboundDownlink": false,
      "statsOutboundUplink": false,
      "statsOutboundDownlink": false
    }
  }
}

启动v2ray

systemctl enable --now v2ray

安装 warp

参考官方.
ubuntu安装, 需要先添加repo再安装, 可以参考官方

# add repo
curl https://pkg.cloudflareclient.com/pubkey.gpg | sudo gpg --yes --dearmor --output /usr/share/keyrings/cloudflare-warp-archive-keyring.gpg

`echo "deb [arch=amd64 signed-by=/usr/share/keyrings/cloudflare-warp-archive-keyring.gpg] https://pkg.cloudflareclient.com/ $(lsb_release -cs) main" | sudo tee /etc/apt/sources.list.d/cloudflare-client.list`

# install
apt install cloudflare-warp

设置warp

warp-cli register  
# 替换为自己的 license key  (optional)
# warp-cli set-license <LICENSE>  
# 切换到 proxy mode  
warp-cli set-mode proxy  
# 修改 socks5 端口，默认 40000  (optional)
# warp-cli set-proxy-port <PORT>  
# 启动  
warp-cli connect
# 自动连接
warp-cli enable-always-on

此时, 应该可以访问到原生IP了, 也就是可以使用chatGPT, 也能顺利观看netflix了. 如果不能观看netflix的话, 可以通过脚本刷IP. 

wget -N https://raw.githubusercontent.com/fscarmen/warp/main/menu.sh && bash menu.sh [option] [lisence]


这里选择11.


模式选择任何一个都可以.
